details:
⭐--Plug and play design, plug and play, worry-free charging
⭐--the charging port is a USB interface, remove the wrist strap, you can directly plug into the USB or charging head, simple and convenient.
⭐--optical heart rate sensor, pay attention to your heart rate changes 24 hours a day
⭐--record your every heart rate change on the YouLife APP, outline your heart rate, and present your health and beauty.
⭐--Larger 1.44-inch display screen with larger and clearer characters, high-sensitivity touch
Warm Remind
1. APP Support System: Android 4.4 and above, IOS above 9.0
2. Do not use a charger higher than 5V/2A.
3. The data cannot be used as medical reference.
4. The watch can't touch the hot water because the hot water would cause the watch display get fog.
USB Quick Removal Direct Charge
Brand new bracelet charging method, quick-release detachable wristband design, can be charged by plugging in the USB interface, eliminating the trouble of carrying a charging cable and charging stand.
Smart Life Assistant
The watch can monitor the steps, calories, heart rate, distance, sleep quality, etc. Of the day. At the same time, it can connected to a smart phone to view information, remotely take pictures, retrieve mobile phones and other thoughtful and convenient functions to make your life more convenient.
Practical
Keep abreast of your exercise intensity and physical condition in order to adjust your fitness plan in a timely manner.
Skin-friendly material
The bracelet wristband is made of lightweight skin-friendly soft TPU, which adopts lightweight design, no feeling to wear.
